thread.title: Neil Millar
thread.title_full: Nelson Alexander reviewed by Neil Millar

author: Neil Millar
title: Neil Millar
text: Sean was very easy to deal with over the course of the negotiations and settlement when we were buying a house through Nelson Alexander. He moved the process quickly and was very responsive to any requests or inquiries during the settlement phase. I found him honest, approachable and transparent and would recommend him as an excellent representative for anyone thinking of selling their property.
